subSections.title: Alternative forms
subSections.text: Due to {{w|Han unification}}, the {{w|Traditional Chinese|traditional form}} containing {{l|mul|冊}} and {{w|Simplified Chinese|simplified form}} containing {{l|mul|册}} are encoded under the same [[code point]]. Depending on the font installed, this character may appear to be either <font size=4.5, lang="zh-hant">粣</font> or <font size=4.5, lang="zh-hans">粣</font>.
